{"tid":112582,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"為了川普離婚　73歲婆婆甩掉結婚22年的老公","createTime":"2017-02-08T08:48:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-08T09:46:55.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8d0f38a4bece3473e918ce2f9781978fdb18a56b","tid":112582,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T08:48:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2321/d2321716.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2321%2Fd2321716.jpg&h=1da21265&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n美國總統川普上任頒布針對7國的移民禁令，除了造成社會分裂也引發夫妻、朋友間的反目，更有一對結婚22年感情融洽的老夫婦，因為彼此政治立場不同而離婚。<br />\n73歲的麥考米克(Gayle McCormick)，是一名加州的退休獄警，長期以來都是支持民主黨的她，雖然與支持共和黨的老公比爾(Bill　McCormick)政治立場不同，但也相安無事共度了22年的婚姻時光，<span style=\"color: red;\">沒想到去年大選因為老公支持川普，而氣到覺得無法跟對方相處，決定提出離婚並分居。</span><br />\n麥考米克認為，無法相信丈夫竟然要去支持一個對女權、種族態度上都這麼差的人，格外感覺自己「被背叛」，立即決定再也不要跟丈夫再生活下去，雖然對方後來改變主意，並沒有真的投給川普，但她已心死稱，「我的餘生再也不需要每周7天、一天24小時去爭論自己的看法了」。<br />\n<br />\n像這樣因為川普而感情生變的案例其實不少，路透/易普索選後一份民調指出，訪問全美6426多人，39%受訪者曾因政治立場與親友爭執、16%民眾表示為了選舉已不再跟朋友或家人談天，更有13%受訪者則是因此完全和某位親友斷絕來往。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文網址: 為了川普離婚　73歲婆婆甩掉結婚22年的老公 | ETtoday國際新聞 | ETtoday 新聞雲 <a href=\"http://www.ettoday.net/news/20170208/862714.htm#ixzz4Y59ITznI \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20170208%2F862714.htm%23ixzz4Y59ITznI%20&d=fAF%2FER2cs4qp%2F6NYk0BreE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=5ea02b8e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ettoday.net/news/20170208/862714.htm#ixzz4Y59ITznI </a><br />\nFollow us: @ETtodaynet on Twitter | ETtoday on Facebook"},{"pid":"3df7b767c0d5499f5f566816fd7d81bc19e54eb0","tid":112582,"uid":45285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T08:54:11.000Z","msg":"婆婆WELL DONE~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7341ffe341248de66fbcbffd3f119baad7511eaa","tid":112582,"uid":55695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T08:56:13.000Z","msg":"恭喜佢老公<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"333848c282fc7a5cfb20d04e620362ed9b93f8a3","tid":112582,"uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T09:07:52.000Z","msg":"Congratulations <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e6cca9bcf6d3c95c061d66bbd8461d417fe1756","tid":112582,"uid":51229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T09:41:15.000Z","msg":"睇死又係feminist<br />\n真係早離早着<br />\n佢老公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93d7da28bf1daad7ee5a505cace5a7db6642515a","tid":112582,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T09:42:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>恭喜佢老公<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"338a3193ebab1e3772585b79bf1ec2c6bb75c2a9","tid":112582,"uid":6267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T09:46:55.000Z","msg":"恭喜佢老公，女權根本on9,<br />\n<br />\n仲嫌讓你唔夠，全部男人去乞食好無"}]}